<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    /* ======================================== */
    /* 1. THEME VARIABLES */
    /* ======================================== */
    :root {
      --primary: #636b2f; /* Dark Green/Olive */
      --secondary: #bac095; /* Light Olive */
      --warning-bg: #fff5f5; /* Light Red for alerts */
      --warning-border: #e53e3e; /* Strong Red for alerts */
      --text-main: #1a1a1a;
      --text-muted: #666;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 2. GLOBAL STYLES & CONTAINER */
    /* ======================================== */
    body { 
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: var(--text-main);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 40px auto; 
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px; /* Consistent rounded corners */
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); /* Soft floating shadow */
      border: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 3. HEADER */
    /* ======================================== */
    .header { 
      background: var(--primary); /* Brand Olive Green */
      color: white; 
      padding: 30px; 
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 4px solid var(--secondary); /* Subtle accent line */
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 4. CONTENT */
    /* ======================================== */
    .content { 
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-main);
    }
    
    /* Security Tips List */
    .content ul {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px 20px 20px 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .content li {
      margin: 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 5. SECURITY NOTICE (The Magic Part) */
    /* ======================================== */
    .security-notice { 
      background: #fff5f5; /* Soft warning red */
      border-left: 4px solid #c53030; /* Darker red accent */
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .security-notice-title {
      color: #c53030;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: block;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .security-notice p {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #2d3748;
    }
    
    /* Emergency Button */
    .btn-emergency {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      background-color: white;
      color: #c53030;
      border: 1px solid #c53030;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .btn-emergency:hover {
      background-color: #c53030;
      color: white;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 6. FOOTER */
    /* ======================================== */
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 20px 30px; 
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #999; 
      font-size: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Password Updated</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>The password for your FormaChat account was successfully changed on <strong>{{changedAt}}</strong>.</p>
      
      <div class="security-notice">
        <span class="security-notice-title">Was this you?</span>
        <p>If you did not make this change, your account may be compromised. Please contact our support team immediately to lock your account.</p>
        <a href="mailto:support@formachat.com?subject=URGENT: Unauthorized Password Change" class="btn-emergency">Contact Support Immediately</a>
      </div>

      <p>If you <strong>did</strong> make this change, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

      <p>For your security, we recommend:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Using a strong, unique password generated by a password manager.</li>
        <li>Enabling two-factor authentication (2FA) if you haven't already.</li>
        <li>Never sharing your password with anyone.</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Stay secure,<br>The FormaChat Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} FormaChat. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Secure System Alert</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>